casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF William Lawrence SUMMERS.
No. D-2944.
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 12, 2016.
William Lawrence Summers, of Cleveland, Ohio, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
